title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Florio/Zimmer/St. Aubin/Johnson/Auman/Russo
description: -- Nordo fills in for PA for the next couple days, Mike Florio opens the show to talk Vikings and their playoff hopes, we hear the Mike Zimmer Presser, Kyndra de St Aubin joins to talk about the Minnesota United loss to Seattle, Ron Johnson talks Vikings and Gophers football, Greg Auman gives insight from Tampa Bay on the Bucs, and Michael Russo talks NHL starting up!
